name: Verify fields displayed after clicking Apply button for "UI/UX Designer" -- @1.1

steps.name: Given I am on the Career landing page
When I click on the dropdown and select "Design team"
And I wait for the job listings to load
Then I click the Apply button for the "UI/UX Designer" job
Then I should see a new page for filling job application details
And I should see "UI/UX Designer" displayed
